d":1065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T22:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身舉美國旗都可以話象徵自由<br />\n舉蘇聯旗俾鬼佬見到真<span style=\"color: red;\">係</span>心諗做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"835b19b2fd6bb45b2c2c3d300a8d48e134715729","tid":1473334,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:34:00.000Z","msg":"用黎做文宣唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n中共在國共內戰時找蘇聯這個外國勢力介入竊國。<br />\n<br />\n江澤民總共出賣了東北地區約300多萬平方公里在歷史上有爭議的疆土給俄國，相當於110個台灣的面積。江還將本屬吉林省的圖們江出海口劃給俄國，從而封死了中國東北通往日本海的唯一出海口。讓正在進行的中俄圖們江出海口問題的談判功虧一簣。這意味著吉林省呼喊多年並投入巨大人力物力財力的「開邊通海戰略」化為烏有。當時琿春土地價格一落千丈，很多投資者遭受重創。江澤民還命令已經從中俄國境線後撤的中國邊防軍再後撤100公里，100公里內不設防。<br />\n<br />\n再問多句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，這難道不是外國勢力嗎?"},{"pid":"966390afc05d508f28f8c79f0c16cfd00f724b0b","tid":1473334,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:36:29.000Z","msg":"我已經準備好大量入貨支那國旗， 10月1號嘗試防唔防火"},{"pid":"f1dc2896976bf29c1258a4212a9bfd126e1580bf","tid":1473334,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:53:25.000Z","msg":"O say does that star-spangled banner yet wave<br />\nO'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sToKWTT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsToKWTT.gif&h=69e4e34c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9201eda9d39bd692700b9ab7460f7bcb8a1d902","tid":1473334,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:55:56.000Z","msg":"USA USA USA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854e6ca488faf7ed8f53326bf7ce2d97fe2902aa","tid":1473334,"uid